@page
@model GuardianCyberStore.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h2 class="font-weight-light text-centre">@ViewData["Title"]</h2>

            <p class="lead mt-4">
                Hey there, cyber warriors! Welcome to GuardianCyberStore, your ultimate fortress against digital threats. We're thrilled to have you join our community dedicated to safeguarding the online world, one byte at a time.
            </p>

            <p>
                GuardianCyberStore wasn't just born out of a business idea; it's a passion project fueled by our team's unwavering commitment to protecting what matters most to you – your digital identity, your privacy, and your peace of mind.
            </p>

            <p>
                Picture this: a group of cybersecurity enthusiasts gathered around a table, fueled by cups of coffee and a shared mission to make the internet a safer place. That's us! We're not just tech geeks; we're real people who understand the importance of keeping you safe in the digital jungle.
            </p>

            <p>
                Our journey began with a simple question: How can we empower individuals and businesses to defend themselves against cyber threats without breaking the bank? And thus, GuardianCyberStore was born – your go-to destination for affordable, user-friendly cybersecurity solutions that pack a punch.
            </p>

            <p>
                What makes GuardianCyberStore stand out? It's not just about selling products; it's about building relationships and fostering a sense of trust. We carefully curate our selection of products and services, handpicking only the best-of-the-best from trusted vendors we know you can rely on.
            </p>

            <p>
                But it doesn't stop there. We're not just here to sell you stuff; we're here to guide you through the murky waters of cybersecurity. Whether you're a tech novice or a seasoned pro, our team is here to offer friendly advice, expert recommendations, and top-notch customer support every step of the way.
            </p>

            <p>
                So, why choose GuardianCyberStore? Because when you shop with us, you're not just a customer – you're part of the Guardian family. Together, let's armor up and take on the digital world with confidence!
            </p>

            <p>
                Have questions, feedback, or just want to say hello? Drop us a line – we'd love to hear from you!
            </p>

            <p class="lead">
                Stay safe, stay secure, and happy shopping!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>